description: This week Rusty Stevens takes on newcomer David Chase. Rusty is back and he's out of control. He's been practicing and he has a few new moves under his belt. David is a big guy and he wants to try out NK. He seems like a nice guy but nice guys finish last here on NK. Will cocky Rusty annihilate David or this is the biggest upset in the history of NK?
title: Rusty Stevens vs David Chase
